@startuml
participant Buyer
participant ClientApplication
participant AccessControlSubsystem
participant DataStorageSubsystem
participant LoggingSubsystem

Buyer -> ClientApplication: Login
ClientApplication -> AccessControlSubsystem: Check Credentials
AccessControlSubsystem -> ClientApplication: Valid
ClientApplication -> LoggingSubsystem: Log Login Event
ClientApplication -> Buyer: Login Successful

Buyer -> ClientApplication: View Product
ClientApplication -> DataStorageSubsystem: Fetch Product Details
DataStorageSubsystem -> ClientApplication: Product Details
ClientApplication -> Buyer: Display Product Details

Buyer -> ClientApplication: Add to Cart
ClientApplication -> DataStorageSubsystem: Add Product to Cart
DataStorageSubsystem -> ClientApplication: Product Added
ClientApplication -> LoggingSubsystem: Log Add to Cart Event
ClientApplication -> Buyer: Product Added to Cart

Buyer -> ClientApplication: Checkout
ClientApplication -> DataStorageSubsystem: Process Order
DataStorageSubsystem -> ClientApplication: Order Confirmation
ClientApplication -> LoggingSubsystem: Log Checkout Event
ClientApplication -> Buyer: Order Confirmed
@enduml
